    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1865-04-10T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1865-04-10T00:00:00-05:00" n="167"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d167">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. F. W. Seward</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Adams</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 1347.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State,</hi>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1865-04-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">April</hi> 10, 1865</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir:</hi> I have to acknowledge the receipt of your
                    despatch of the 24th of March, No. 908, together with a copy of the Times,
                    containing a report of the proceedings in both houses of Parliament on the
                    evening of the 23d ultimo, from which it is evident that the tone of the British
                    ministry towards this government is much changed. The indications of a more just
                    appreciation of American affairs in England are received with satisfaction.</p>
                <p>I am, sir, your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>F. W. SEWARD, <hi rend="italic">Acting Secretary.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Charles Francis Adams,</hi> Esq., <hi rend="italic"
                            >&amp;c., &amp;c., &amp;c.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
